==Books==
* ''Girl in the Attic'' (2002)
* ''Coming of Age'' (2003)
* ''Lost and Found'' (2004)
* ''The Drowning'' (2005)
* ''Larkswood'' (2011)
* ''The Hideaway'' (2015)

===Picture Books===
* ''Tomasina's First Dance'' (1992)
* ''Look At Me, Grandma!'' (2001)

